PrecisEnactment of the TRENTON AIRPORT ZONING REGULATIONS which impose the usual kinds of restrictions on the manner in which land located within a four- kilometre radius of the airfield known as Trenton Airport, in the Township of Sidney, Ontario, may be used or developed.
